        testing
          reached:step_2
          censused,uno=6,duo=3
          see:two collections stand divided on one shared disk — each Pier holds only its own artists as whole original bytes
          reached:seal
          sealed
          reached:job_uno
          see:the pair sealed over the wire — a mutual Music grant gates the heist both ways
          see:a heist job stands pointed at the pier — its filing decisions pinned before any byte crossed
          offered:uno,n=3
          manifest:uno,fresh=3
          heisted:uno,landed=3,faithful=3,took_named=3,streamed
            on_disk:4t-mathrock/Fourier Four - Bogus Name.wav,bytes=8110
            on_disk:4t-mathrock/Fourier Four - Echo E.wav,bytes=960104
            on_disk:4t-mathrock/Fourier Four - Query E.wav,bytes=1088104
          reached:job_duo
          see:the heist landed straight into the collection — every file byte-faithful to its source hash on the disk
          see:the landing filed by category — each track under the genre its filing named
          see:a mislabeled file kept its own name on disk — the catalog knew the truth from the tags but a cp never renames the file
          see:the landing streamed chunk by chunk — no whole track ever waited in memory
          offered:duo,n=9
          manifest:duo,holds=3,fresh=6
          heisted:duo,landed=6,skipped=3,faithful=6
            on_disk:4t-bangers/DJ Oscillo - Cosmic C.wav,bytes=1248104
            on_disk:4t-bangers/DJ Oscillo - Dorian D.wav,bytes=1216104
            on_disk:4t-bangers/DJ Oscillo - Groove G.wav,bytes=1056104
