            on_disk:4t-chillwave/The Sines - Middle A.wav,bytes=1024102
          reached:job_reuno
          see:the mirror heist landed the other way — each end filed the same disk under its own categories
          offered:reuno,n=9
          manifest:reuno,holds=9
          see:the manifest named every verdict before a byte moved — the heist showed what it would take and what it already held
          heisted:reuno,skipped=9,held_named=9
          see:a second heist found nothing new — the catalog identity of every offer was already held
          see:every offer left a named verdict on the job — took or held each pointed by tune
          mag_pub:held,cards=9
          see:Uno published its whole collection as a magazine — every landed track rode in as a record keeping its own path and hash
          reached:logs
          newlyadded_shape,uno=3,duo=6,unsourced
          see:newlyadded logs each arrival with a fresh feeling — and never a word about the source
          reached:deny
          denied,gone,carded_off,log_dropped
          see:a denied track left the collection — the file gone and the log honest about the drop
          mag_pub:recast,cards=8
          see:a republish recast the real magazine in step with the collection — the denied track left the magazine too and no orphan stayed behind
          reached:flat
          flattened
          see:the scaffolding flattened away — no heist stands and nothing attributes who gave what
